CHAT.comment: Chi and Mot are having breakfast as they discuss first what Chi is going to do at school that day. The two also discuss their upcoming Christmas plans which include an early Christmas dinner with family friends and then a trip to Florida to see Chi's grandparents. Throughout the mealtime , both Chi and Mot talk to the dog , Toby , with affection , and tease her as well. Chi also brings up the topic of games on CD Rom , which he would like as a Christmas present. Mot is concerned about the violence in these games , and Chi suggests some games which may not be as violent. Finally , Chi begins to whine about eating school lunches , especially about the difficulty of eating a meatless meal at school , since Chi is a vegetarian. Mot and Chi finally conclude that Chi should start to bring more home lunches. Mot and Chi seem to have a good relationship. They both are pretty calm and respectful to one another throughout the mealtime.
